thread.title: Starbucks Corp. Earnings -- What to Watch

author: Julie Jargon
title: Starbucks Corp. Earnings -- What to Watch
text:
Starbucks Corp. is scheduled to report fiscal second-quarter results after the market closes on Thursday. Here is what you need to know.
EARNINGS FORECAST: Analysts polled by FactSet expect profit of 53 cents a share, compared with 45 cents per share a year ago.
